casebody.data:
Commissioners of the State Insurance Fund, Appellants, v. Rivington Farm Dairy, Inc., Respondent.

(Republished)

Judgment dismissing the complaint unanimously reversed, on the law and the facts, with costs to plaintiffs, and judgment granted in favor of plaintiffs for $575.56, with interest and costs. Settle order on notice. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, Rabin, Valente and McNally, JJ. [16 AD 2d 58.]
